692
00:56:52,555 --> 00:56:54,140
Kuberi tahu agar waktumu tak sia-sia.

693
00:56:54,724 --> 00:56:56,309
Jika kau punya waktu mengejarku,

694
00:56:56,392 --> 00:56:58,436
