698
00:57:14,535 --> 00:57:16,162
Tapi ada juga hari-hari

699
00:57:17,455 --> 00:57:18,789
saat aku tak bisa berhenti

700
00:57:19,457 --> 00:57:21,500
memikirkannya sepanjang hari,

701
00:57:22,668 --> 00:57:26,380
