715
00:59:41,557 --> 00:59:43,309
<i>Kau akan kembali ke Yunani?</i>

716
00:59:44,560 --> 00:59:46,353
<i>Semoga penerbanganmu lancar.</i>

717
00:59:47,354 --> 00:59:48,898
<i>Kuharap kita tak bertemu lagi.</i>

718
00:59:50,483 --> 00:59:51,484
Cha-young!

719
01:00:25,726 --> 01:00:28,312
<i>Mari berhenti membicarakan Min-seong,</i>

720
01:00:29,230 --> 01:00:30,314
<i>masa lalumu,</i>

721
01:00:31,315 --> 01:00:32,983
